programme.title: James Martin: Home Comforts at Christmas
programme.desc: From the comfort of his own home James creates recipes that are packed full of goodness to help you recover from festive overindulgence! Special guest Glynn Purnell.

programme.title: The Pioneer Woman
programme.desc: Award-winning blogger and best-selling cookbook author Ree Drummond shares her special brand of home cooking from down on the ranch. She creates menus for every occasion, from last-minute family suppers to elegant celebrations.

programme.title: The Pioneer Woman
programme.desc: Ree Drummond cooks some no-fail fall favourites, starting with an Autumn Steak Salad and a one-pan Fall Chicken Skillet. Then, she prepares Santa Fe Eggs in Purgatory for an all-day breakfast and her quick Mini Chocolate Tarts.

programme.title: The Hairy Bikers Home for Christmas
programme.sub-title: Paul Martin / Christmas Without Overdoing It
programme.desc: The Bikers share some meat-free recipes perfect for when youve had enough of turkey. Today they create sage and spinach gnocchi, nut roast with all the trimmings and a hazelnut and pear cake as they find out how Paul spends his Christmas.

programme.title: The Great British Bake Off Masterclass
programme.desc: Taking inspiration from all over Europe for the festive season, Mary and Paul put a twist on British Christmas favourites. Paul kicks off the baking with St Lucia buns, and Mary makes a white chocolate and stem ginger cheesecake.

programme.title: Jamies Family Christmas
programme.desc: Its all about roasties with the mosties as Jamie is joined by Gennaro Contaldo, to show how to make the very best roast potatoes and exciting Christmas vegetables; plus lovely leftover recipes. First off, Jamie shows how to make perfect roast potatoes every time - golden, crispy on the outside, soft and fluffy on the inside. The secret is to use Maris Piper potatoe.

programme.title: Jamies Family Christmas
programme.desc: Jamie prepares some exciting alternatives to traditional Christmas desserts. Mum Sally joins Jamie in the kitchen to make a killer chocolate mousse: and she reminds him how excited he was as a kid at Christmas, especially when he got a drum kit! Jamies Winter Pudding Bombe is a Christmas take on summer pudding, with panatone, ice cream, crystalised fruit and sherry. Just bang it in the freezer and hey presto.
